{
  "id": "99e2b42ec6154a88b53c77e7188b7d43",
  "title": "Simple Gravity Fields",
  "description": "A toolkit for easy to use Gravitational Areas!",
  "longDescription": "<h2>INFORMATION: This Product has been removed from Sale starting 31.01.2022</h2><p><br /></p><p>Legacy Documentation available on <a href=\"https://divivor.itch.io/old-docs\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://divivor.itch.io/old-docs</a> (Use password: legacydocs)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>______________________________</p><p><br /></p><p>The Simple Gravity Fields (in short: SGF) is a toolkit for easy to use Gravitational Areas. It provides you with a basic set of Blueprint Actors and Components to find and create custom Gravity Directions.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Important: </strong><em>This Asset does not provide a complete Game Mechanic, only the necessary tools to use directional Gravity! It also does not provide support for default UE4 Character Movement!</em></p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li>Adjustable and smooth Gravity direction changes</li><li>Support for overlapping Gravity Areas</li><li>Overridable Priority per Area (Lower Priority Areas get ignored)</li><li>Overridable Gravity Strength per Area</li><li>Support for multiple Gravity Centers on Actors</li><li>Gravity Area Finder Component</li><li>Custom Gravity Component for Physics</li><li>Visual Indicators for easy level editing</li><li>Includes a Demo Map</li><li>100% Made in Blueprints</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>9 Gravity Areas:</strong></p><ul><li>Directional</li><li>Spline and Directional Spline</li><li>Cylindrical and Inverted</li><li>Spherical and Inverted</li><li>Quarter Cylindrical and Inverted (Useful for Ramps)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 19</p>",
